<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.9">
<l>moyttukkaṇpaṉi cōrameykaḷci lirppavēṅki yiḷaittuniṉ</l>
<l>ṟeyttukkumpiṭu naṭṭamiṭṭeḻun tāṭippāṭiyi ṟaiñciyeṉ</l>
<l>ṉattaṉacca ṉaraṅkaṉukkaṭi yārkaḷāki yavaṉukkē</l>
<l>pittarāmavar pittarallarkaṇ maṟṟaiyārmuṟṟum pittarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the eyes exude tears that crowd together as [their] bodies bristle,</l>
<l>pining, standing exhausted, growing weary, performing a worship dance,</l>
<l>rising, dancing, singing, bowing [and] becoming the servants of</l>
<l rend="indent">my Father, [my] Lord, Raṅga,</l>
<l>they who are solely mad on Him are not madmen,</l>
<l>[it is] the others who are complete madmen.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
